title: Tripoli
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Old-school, traditional, casual Lebanese restaurant. Has many vegetable-based dishes such as lentils and bulgur wheat, black eyed pea and celery, eggplant and potato, couscous, baba ganoush, hummus, mezze platter with falafel, tabouli salad, pita (baked in-house). Pickles radishes and olives which served with the appetizers.
